quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Twa Seen Meem
  26,2,Lawa ngamavesi encwadi ecacile
  26,3,Siyazi ukuthi wena uphatheka kabi emphefumulweni ngenxa yokuthi abakholwa
  26,4,Uma sithanda singehlisela phezu kwabo uphawu oluvela ezulwini oluzokwenza ukuthi kugobe izintamo zabo ngokuzithoba
  26,5,Futhi angeke kufike kubona isikhumbuzo esisha esivela (kuMvelinqangi)onomusangaphandlekokubabayasifulathela
  26,6,Ngakho-ke ngempela bayenqaba (incwadi) ziyofika kubona izindaba zalokho ababenza inhlekisa ngako
  26,7,Ababheki yini emhlabeni ukuthi zingaki izinhlobo zezinto esenza ukuthi zimile kuwona na
  26,8,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo aliyibona abakholwayo
  26,9,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,10,Futhi (khumbula) ngenkathi iNkosi yakho ibiza uMose ukuthi akahambe aye kubantu abayizoni”
  26,11,"Abantu baFaro, ngakube abamesabi yini uMvelinqangi na"
  26,12,"Wathi, “Nkosi yami ngempela mina ngiyesaba ukuthi bazongiphika.”"
  26,13,Futhi isifuba sami siyacinana nolimi lwami alukhulumi kahle ngakho-ke thumela ukuthi kulandwe u-Aroni
  26,14,"Futhi mina nginecala kubona, ngakho-ke ngiyesaba ukuthi bazongibulala"
  26,15,"Wathi, “Qha hambani nobabili nezimpawu zethu ngempela thina sikanye nani, siyezwa”"
  26,16,Ngakho-ke hambani nobabili uma senifikile kuFaro nithi “thina siyizithunywa zeNkosi yemihlaba”
  26,17,Ngakho-ke bavumele abantwana bakwa-Israyeli bahambe kanye nathi
  26,18,"(UFaro) wathi (kuMose), “asizange yini sikukhulise phakathi kwethu njengomntwana futhi wahlala kanye nathi iminyaka eminingi yempilo yakho na?”"
  26,19,Futhi wenza isenzo sakho owasenza kulapho wena wawungomunye wabangabongi
  26,20,Wathi (uMose) “ngakwenza lokho ngenkathi mina ngangingomunye wabasephutheni”
  26,21,Ngakho-ke ngabaleka kunina ngenkathi nginesaba kepha iNkosi yami yangipha isehlulelo futhi yangenza ngaba ngomunye wezithunywa
  26,22,Futhi ngakube (iwona lowo) umusa ongikhumbuzisa wona ukuthi wagqilaza abantwana bakwa Israyeli na?”
  26,23,UFaro (Wabuza) wathi “futhi iyini iNkosi yemihlaba na?”
  26,24,(UMose waphendula) ngokuthi “iNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili uma kungukuthi nifuna ukuqiniseka”
  26,25,(UFaro) wathi “kulabo ababemzungezile “ngakube anikuzwa yini (lokho akushoyo) na?”
  26,26,"Wathi, “iNkosi yenu neNkosi yoyihlo basendulo”"
  26,27,"(UFaro) wathi, “ngempela isithunywa senu lesi esithunywe kunina siyahlanya”"
  26,28,"(UMose) wathi, “iNkosi yeMpumalanga neNtshonalanga kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili uma kungukuthi nina ninayo ingqondo”"
  26,29,"(UFaro) wathi, “uma ukhetha omunye uNkulunkulu esikhundleni sami ngempela ngizokwenza ukuthi ube ngomunye weziboshwa”"
  26,30,"UMose wathi, “yize noma ngingakulethela into esobala na?”"
  26,31,"(UFaro) wathi, “ilethe uma wena ungomunye wabaneqiniso”"
  26,32,Ngakho-ke (uMose) waphonsa phansi induku yakhe kwaba yilapho iphenduka inyoka egqamile
  26,33,Futhi wakhipha isandla sakhe kwaba yilapho simhlophe kwabasibonayo
  26,34,"(UFaro) wathi, ebaholini abamzungelezile ngempela lona ngumlumbi onolwazi olunzulu"
  26,35,Ufuna ukunigxosha ezweni lenu ngomlingo wakhe nicabanga ukuthi kwenziwe njani
  26,36,"Bathi, “mnike ithuba yena nomfowabo bese uthumela izigijimi emadolobheni”"
  26,37,Ukuze zikulethele bonke abalumbi abanolwazi olunzulu
  26,38,Ngakho-ke abalumbi baqoqelwa ndawonye ukuze kuqokwe isikhathi ngosuku olwaziwayo
  26,39,Futhi kwathiwa kubantu ngakube nina niyohlangana ndawonye na
  26,40,Ukuze sibalandele abelumbi uma bona bengabanqobayo
  26,41,"Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebefika abalumbi bathi kuFaro, “ngakube sizowuthola yini umvuzo uma thina singabanqobayo na?”"
  26,42,"UFarowathi,“yebofuthingempelaninanizobangabasondelayo (kumina)”"
  26,43,"UMose wathi kubona, “phonsani lokho enizokuphonsa”"
  26,44,"Ngakho-ke baziphonsa izintambo zabo kanye nezinduku zabo base bethi, “ngamandla kaFaro ngempela thina sizonqoba”"
  26,45,Ngakho-ke uMose wayiphonsa phansi induku yakhe kwaba yilapho – yona ikugwinya konke lokho okungamanga ababekuveza
  26,46,Ngakho-ke bawa abelumbi bajabalala
  26,47,"Bathi, “sikholiwe eNkosini yemihlaba”"
  26,48,In kosi kaMose no-Aroni”
  26,49,"(UFaro) wathi, “senikholiwe kuyona ngaphambi kokuba ngininike imvume ngempela yena (uMose) iyiNkosi yenu okuyiyona eyanifundisa umlingo ngakho-ke nizokwazi, ngempela ngizonquma izandla zenu kanye nezinyawo zenu ezinhlangothini ezehlukene futhi ngempela ngizoninqamuleza nonke”"
  26,50,"Bathi, “abukho ubungozi (asesabi lutho) ngempela thina siyophindela eNkosini yethu”"
  26,51,Siyethemba ukuthi iNkosi yethu izosithethelala ukona kwethu ngokuba singamakholwa okuqala”
  26,52,Futhi sembula kuMose ukuthi akahambe ebusuku kanye nezinceku zami ngempela nina nizolandelwa
  26,53,Ngakho-ke uFaro wathumela izigijimi emadolobheni
  26,54,Ngempela laba bayiqembu elincane
  26,55,Futhi ngempela bona bayasithukuthelisa
  26,56,Futhi ngempela thina saqaphelisa wonke umphakathi
  26,57,Ngakho-ke sabakhipha ezivandeni nasemithonjeni
  26,58,"Nasemicebweni\tnakuzona\tzonke\tizinhlobo\tzezindawo ezihloniphekile"
  26,59,Kanjalo sakunikeza lokho njengefa kubantwana bakwa- Israyeli
  26,60,Ngakho-ke babalandela ngasekuphumeni kwelanga
  26,61,"Kwathi lapho amaqembu amabili esebonana abalandeli baMose bathi, “ngempela sesificiwe”"
  26,62,"(UMose) wathi, “lutho! Ngempela iNkosi yami ikanye nami izongihola”"
  26,63,"Ngakho-ke sembula kuMose ukuthi, “shaya ulwande ngenduku yakho” lwaqhekeka phakathi ingxenye nengxenye yaphenduka yaba yigquma elikhulu elinjengentaba"
  26,64,Futhi sabasondeza abanye lapho
  26,65,Futhi samsindisa uMose kanye nababekanye naye bonke
  26,66,Sabe sesiyabaminzisa abanye
  26,67,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo alisibona abakholwayo
  26,68,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,69,Futhi bafundele indaba ka-Abrahamu
  26,70,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\tethi\tkuyise\tnakubantu\tbakhe, “nikhonzani na?”"
  26,71,"Bathi, “sikhonza izithombe, sizinikele kuzona.”"
  26,72,"(U-Abrahamu) wathi, “ngakube ziyanizwa yini uma nizibiza na?”"
  26,73,Noma ziwusizo kunina noma zinobungozi na
  26,74,"Bathi, “Qhabo! Safica obaba bethu benzenjalo (bezikhonza izithixo).”"
  26,75,"U-Abrahamu wathi, “Ngakube nikubonile yini lokho nina enanikukhonza”"
  26,76,Nina kanye naboyihlo basendulo na
  26,77,Ngakho-ke ngempela bona bayizitha kumina ngaphandle kweNkosi yemihlaba
  26,78,"Okuyiyona eyangidalayo, yona iyangihola"
  26,79,Futhi iyona engipha ukudla nengiphuzisayo
  26,80,Futhi uma ngigula yona iyangelapha
  26,81,Futhi iyona eyokwenza ukuthi ngife bese ingipha ukuphila
  26,82,Futhi iyona engethemba ukuthi iyongithethelela amaphutha ami ngosuku lwenkokhelo
  26,83,Nkosi yami ngiphe ukwehlulela (ukuhola okuyiqiniso) futhi ungihlanganise nabalungileyo
  26,84,Futhi ngiphe udumo ezizukulwaneni ezilandelayo
  26,85,"Futhi\tngenze\tngibe\tngomunye\twezindlalifa\tzesivande senjabulo"
  26,86,"Futhi\tthethelela\tubaba\tngempela\tyena\tungomunye wabadukileyo"
  26,87,Futhi ungangiphathi kabi ngosuku lapho beyobe bevuswa
  26,88,Ngosuku lapho umnotho nezingane kungeke kusize ngalutho
  26,89,"Ngaphandle\tkwalowo\toyoza\tkuMvelinqangi\tnenhliziyo emsulwa"
  26,90,Futhi izulu liyosondezelwa abesaba uMvelinqangi
  26,91,Futhi isihogo siyovezelwa obala labo abaphambukileyo
  26,92,"Futhi kuyothiwa kubona, “kuphi lokho enanikukhonza na?”"
  26,93,Esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi na? Ngakube kuyanisiza noma kuyazisiza na
  26,94,Ngakho-ke bayophonswa kusona (isihogo) bona kanye nabaphambukileyo
  26,95,Kanye namabutho kasathane wonke
  26,96,Lapho phakathi bona bayoxabana bathi
  26,97,Sifunga ngoMvelinqangi! Ngempela sasisekudukeni okucacile
  26,98,Ngenkathi sinilinganisa neNkosi yemihlaba
  26,99,Futhi akekho owasidukisa ngaphandle kwezoni
  26,100,Ngakho-ke asinaye ongomunye wabancengeli
  26,101,Noma umngane omnene
  26,102,Ngakho-ke ukube besingaphindela (emhlabeni) besizokuba ngabanye babakholwayo
  26,103,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo alikholwa
  26,104,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,105,Abantu baNowa baziphika izithunywa
  26,106,"Khumbula ngenkathi umfowabo uNowa ethi kubona, “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi?”"
  26,107,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,108,Ngakho-ke mesabeni uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,109,"Futhi angiwuceli kunina umvuzo ngako, umvuzo wami angiwutholi (komunye umuntu) ngaphandle kokuwucela eNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,110,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,111,"Bathi, “singakholelwa yini kuwena kulapho ulandelwa ngabantu abasezingeni eliphansi kakhulu na?”"
  26,112,Wathi. “Futhi yiluphi ulwazi enginalo ngalokho ababekwenza na?”
  26,113,Ukwahlulelwa kwabo kuseNkosini yami ukube nje benazi
  26,114,Futhi angeke ngiwagxoshe amakholwa
  26,115,Mina angiyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumxwayisi ocacile
  26,116,"Bathi, “uma ungaphezi Oh Nowa! Ngempela uzokuba ngomunye walabo abakhandwa ngamatshe”"
  26,117,"(UNowa) wathi, “Nkosi yami ngempela abantu bami bangiphika.”"
  26,118,Ngakho-ke yehlulela phakathi kwami nabo futhi ungisindise kanye nanoma ngabe ngobani abakanye nami abangamakholwa
  26,119,"Ngakho-ke\tsamsindisa\tkanye\tnalabo\tabakanye\tnaye emkhunjini othweleyo"
  26,120,Sabe sesibaminzisa abanye emva kwalokho
  26,121,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo lalingesiwona amakholwa
  26,122,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,123,Abantu base A’d baziphika izithunywa
  26,124,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\tumfowabo\tuHud\tethi\tkubona “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi?”"
  26,125,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,126,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphile
  26,127,"Futhi angiwufuni umvuzo kunina ngako, umvuzo wami angiwutholi komunye umuntu ngaphandle kokuwuthola eNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,128,Ngakube nenza uphawu phezu kwazo zonke izindawo eziphakeme? Niyazithokozisa
  26,129,Futhi nizithathele izindlu ezinkulu ezidephile ezinohlonze ukuze nihlale kuzona ingunaphakade
  26,130,"Futhi uma nishaya, nishaya ngobudlova"
  26,131,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,132,Futhi mesabeni lowo owanilekelela ngalokho enikwaziyo
  26,133,Wanilekelela ngezinkomo nangezingane
  26,134,Nangezivande nangemithombo
  26,135,Ngempela mina ngiyanesabela isijeziso sosuku olukhulu
  26,136,"Bathi,\t“kuyefana\tkuthina\tnoma\tuyashumayela\tnoma awusiyena omunye wabashumayelayo”"
  26,137,"Lokhu\takuyilutho\tngaphandle\tkokuba\tkube\tyinkolo yasendulo"
  26,138,Futhi thina angeke sijeziswe
  26,139,"Ngakho-ke bamphika sabe sesibabhubhisa, ngempela kulokho kunophawu futhi iningi labo lalingesiwona amakholwa"
  26,140,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,141,Abantu baThamud baziphika izithunywa
  26,142,Khumbula ngenkathi umfowabo uSwalih ethi kubona “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi.”
  26,143,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,144,Ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,145,"Futhi angiwufuni kunina umvuzo ngako, umvuzo wami awukho komunye umuntu ngaphandle kokuba useNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,146,Ngakube nizoyekwa niphephile kulokhu enikukona lapha
  26,147,Ezivandeni nasemithonjeni
  26,148,Nasemasimini nasezihlahleni zesundu isixha sazo sithambile
  26,149,Futhi nimba izintaba ngobiciko ukuze nakhe izindlu
  26,150,Ngakho-ke mesabeni uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,151,Futhi ningayihloniphi impoqo yezaphulamthetho
  26,152,"Labo abenza ukona ezweni, abangalungisi"
  26,153,"Bathi, “kuphela wena ungomunye wabalunjiwe”"
  26,154,Awuyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumuntu onjengathi ngakho-ke makunjalo veza uphawu uma kungukuthi wena ungomunye wabaqinisile
  26,155,"Wathi, “leli yikameli lensikazi linelungelo lokuphuza, nani ninelungelo lokuphuza ngosuku olwaziwayo”"
  26,156,Futhi ningalithinti ngobubi hleze nithathwe yisijeziso sosuku olukhulu
  26,157,Kepha balibulala (ikameli) base bephenduka abazisolayo
  26,158,"Ngakho-ke\tbathathwa\tyisijeziso,\tngempela\tkulokho kunesifundo futhi iningi labo lalingeyibona abakholwayo"
  26,159,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,160,Abantu baLothi baziphika izithunywa
  26,161,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\tumfowabo\tuLothi\tethi\tkubona “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi?”"
  26,162,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,163,Ngakho-ke mesabeni uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,164,"Futhi angiwufuni kunina umvuzo ngako, umvuzo wami awukho komunye umuntu ngaphandle kokuthi useNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,165,Ngakube phakathi kwezidalwa (nikhetha) ukuya kwabesilisa na
  26,166,"Futhi niyeka labo iNkosi yenu eyanidalela bona ukuba babe ngamakhosikazi enu, Qhabo! Nina ningabantu abephula umthetho"
  26,167,"Bathi, “Oh Lothi! uma ungaphezi ngempela uzokuba ngomunye wabagxoshiwe”"
  26,168,"Wathi, “Ngempela mina lesisenzo senu angisithandi”"
  26,169,Nkosi yami ngisindise kanye nomndeni wami kulokhu abakwenzayo
  26,170,Ngakho-ke samsindisa kanye nomndeni wakhe wonke
  26,171,Ngaphandle konkosikazi omdala phakathi kwalabo ababesalele ngemumva
  26,172,Sabe sesibabhubhisa abanye
  26,173,"Futhi sayinethisa imvula phezu kwabo, imvula eyayiyimbi kulabo ababexwayisiwe"
  26,174,Ngempelakulokhukunesifundofuthiiningilabolalingesiwona amakholwa
  26,175,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,176,Izihlali zase-Aykah zaziziphika izithunywa
  26,177,Khumbula ngenkathi uShuaib ethi kuzona “animesabi yini na uMvelinqangi?”
  26,178,Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esethembekile kunina
  26,179,Ngakho-ke mesabeni uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe
  26,180,"Futhi angiwufuni kunina umvuzo ngako, umvuzo wami angiwutholi komunye umuntu ngaphandle kokuwuthola eNkosini yemihlaba"
  26,181,Nikezani isilinganiso esigcwele futhi ningabi ngabanye balabo abayimbangela yokulahleka
  26,182,Futhi linganisani ngesikalo esiyiqiniso nesiqondile
  26,183,Futhi ningayidli impahla yabantu ngamacebo ngokuyehlisa futhi ningenzi ukona emhlabeni
  26,184,"Futhi\tmesabeni\tlowo\towanidala\tkanye\tnezizukulwane zasendulo"
  26,185,"Bathi, “kuphela wena ungomunye walabo abalunjiwe”"
  26,186,Futhi wena awuyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngumuntu ofananathi futhi sicabanga ukuthi ungomunye wabaqamba amanga
  26,187,Ngakho-ke makunjalo yehlisela phezu kwethu ingxenye yezulu uma kungukuthi ungomunye wabaqinisileyo
  26,188,"Wathi, “iNkosi yami eyazi kangcono ngaloko enikwenzayo”"
  26,189,"Kepha bamphika, ngakho-ke yisijeziso sosuku lwethunzi, ngempela leso kwakuyisijeziso sosuku olukhulu"
  26,190,"Ngempela\tkulokho\tkunesifundo\tfuthi\tiningi\tlabo lalingeyiwona amakholwa"
  26,191,Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho yona iphakeme ngamandla inesihawu
  26,192,Futhi ngempela lesi yisambulo seNkosi yemihlaba
  26,193,"Esehliselwe\tphansi\tngumoya\tongcwele\t(uGabriyeli) owethembekile"
  26,194,Enhliziyweni yakho ukuze ube ngomunye wabaxwayisi
  26,195,Ngolimi lwesi-Arabhu olucacile
  26,196,Futhi ngempela yona (iQur’an) kwakubikezelwe ngayo emibhalweni yasemandulo
  26,197,Akusilona yini uphawu kubona ukuthi izifundiswa zabantwana bakwa-Israyeli ziyayazi (iQur’an) na
  26,198,Ngisho noma ngabe sasiyembule kwabanye bakwelinye izwe
  26,199,Bese eyabafundela babengeke babe ngabakholelwa kuyona
  26,200,Kanjalo sayenza ukuthi ingene igxile ezinhliziyweni zezoni
  26,201,Abakholelwa kuyona kuze kube yilapho bebona khona isijeziso esibuhlungu
  26,202,Ngakho-ke siyobafikela masinyane kulapho bona benganakile
  26,203,"Bayothi, “ngakube thina sizonikwa yini na ithuba?”"
  26,204,Ngakube basafuna yini ukusisheshisa isijeziso sethu na
  26,205,"Ngakube\tubonile\tyini\tukuthi\tsabathokozisa\timinyaka eminingi na"
  26,206,Kwabe sekufika kubona lokho ababethenjiswe kona na
  26,207,Akuzange kubasize lokho ababezijabulisa ngako
  26,208,Futhi alikho idolobha esalibhubhisa elalingenabo abexwayisi balo
  26,209,"Ngendlela\teyisikhumbuzo,\tfuthi\tasikaze\tsenze okungenabulungiswa"
  26,210,Futhi akuyibona osathane abayiletha phansi(iQuran)
  26,211,Futhi akubafanele (osathane ukwenza lokho) futhi abanawo amandla
  26,212,Ngempela bona baqhelelanisiwe nokuzwa
  26,213,"Ngakho-ke\tungambizi\tuMvelinqangi\tkanye\tnomunye uNkulunkulu ngokuba uzoba ngomunye wabajeziswayo"
  26,214,Futhi zixwayise izihlobo zakho ezisondele kakhulu
  26,215,Futhi yiba mnene kunoma ngabe ngubani okulandelayo kwabakholwayo
  26,216,"Kepha uma bengakuhloniphi ngakho-ke ithi, “ngempela mina ngimsulwa kulokho enikwenzayo”"
  26,217,Futhi thembela kophakeme ngamandla onesihawu
  26,218,Lowo okubonayo uma usukuma emthandazweni
  26,219,Nokuhamba phakathi kwalabo abaguqile bezithobile
  26,220,"Ngempela yena ungozwayo, owaziyo"
  26,221,Ngakube nginitshelile yini ukuthi osathane behlela phezu kukabani na
  26,222,Behlela phezu kwabona bonke abaqamba amanga abanezono
  26,223,Bayamlalela (usathane) futhi iningi labo lingabaqambimanga
  26,224,"Kanye nezimbongi, abaphambukayo bayazilandela"
  26,225,Awuboni yini ukuthi bona bayazulazula kuzona zonke izigodi
  26,226,Nokuthi bona basho lokho abangakwenzi
  26,227,Ngaphandle kwalabo abakholwayo abenza izenzo ezilungileyo futhi abakhumbula uMvelinqangi kaningi futhi abavikelayo emva kokuba benziwe okungenabulungiswa futhi bayokwazi labo abenza okungenabo ubulungiswa ukuthi iyiphi indawo yokuphenduka abayophendukela kuyona